OL,4,CDWP sees 'sharp rise' in benefit death
OL,5,Creviews
OL,6, The number of internal reviews held
OL,7, when a person claiming benefits dies or
OL,8, comes to serious harm has risen in the
OL,9, past two years, new figures show.
OL,11,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,12,F(DWP) has begun 124 reviews since July
OL,13,F2019. Ninety-seven of those concerned
OL,14,Fpeople who died.
OL,16,FThe DWP holds reviews when it is
OL,17,Falleged its actions had a negative
OL,18,Fimpact, or when named at an inquest.
OL,20,FIt said its priority was to deliver a
OL,21,Fsupportive and compassionate service.
